'''拉斯維加斯大獎賽'''是一個計劃舉辦的一級方程式大獎賽，它將成為[[2023年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2023年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的一部分，<ref name="official name">{{Cite web |title=Las Vegas to host Formula 1 night race from 2023 |url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.breaking-las-vegas-to-host-formula-1-night-race-from-2023.69O9nKLwKraqAhR5rr8TQg.html |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=Formula 1® |language=en |archive-date=2022-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331024136/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.breaking-las-vegas-to-host-formula-1-night-race-from-2023.69O9nKLwKraqAhR5rr8TQg.html }}</ref>該賽事在[[內華達州|內華達州]][[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]中[[拉斯維加斯大道|拉斯維加斯大道]]的[[拉斯維加斯街道賽道|拉斯維加斯街道賽道]]上舉行。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |title=LAS VEGAS GRAND PRIX: Everything you need to know about F1’s newest race |url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.las-vegas-grand-prix-everything-you-need-to-know-about-f1s-newest-race.7HD0mpbF6pjSFsNatKZTwH.html |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=Formula 1® |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220603092556/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.las-vegas-grand-prix-everything-you-need-to-know-about-f1s-newest-race.7HD0mpbF6pjSFsNatKZTwH.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Las Vegas Grand Prix confirmed for Formula 1 calendar in 2023 |url=https://www.cnbc.com/2022/03/31/las-vegas-grand-prix-confirmed-for-formula-1-calendar-in-2023.html |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=www.cnbc.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408015245/https://www.cnbc.com/2022/03/31/las-vegas-grand-prix-confirmed-for-formula-1-calendar-in-2023.html }}</ref> 

== 歷史 ==
2022年3月，外間已經有傳聞拉斯維加斯將會重返一級方程式賽事。<ref>{{Cite web |date=2022-03-24 |title=Formula 1 Coming to Las Vegas |url=https://frontofficesports.com/formula-1-coming-to-las-vegas/ |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=Front Office Sports |language=en-US |archive-date=2022-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422075647/https://frontofficesports.com/formula-1-coming-to-las-vegas/ }}</ref> 拉斯維加斯上一次舉辦一級方程式大獎賽已經是在{{F1|1982}}的[[凱撒宮大獎賽|凱撒宮大獎賽]]。<ref>{{Cite web |title=F1 to return to Las Vegas with Saturday night race in 2023 |url=https://www.autosport.com/f1/news/f1-to-return-to-las-vegas-with-saturday-night-race-in-2023/9462604/ |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=www.autosport.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220524143913/https://www.autosport.com/f1/news/f1-to-return-to-las-vegas-with-saturday-night-race-in-2023/9462604/ }}</ref> 大獎賽預計將於2023年11月感恩節在拉斯維加斯大道附近舉行。<ref name=":0" /> 這將是在F1賽曆中的第三個在美國舉辦的大獎賽。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Las Vegas to become third American F1 grand prix venue in 2023 |url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2022/mar/31/las-vegas-to-become-third-american-f1-grand-prix-venue-in-2023 |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=www.theguardian.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220624042135/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2022/mar/31/las-vegas-to-become-third-american-f1-grand-prix-venue-in-2023 }}</ref> （其餘兩個分別是[[美國大獎賽|美國大獎賽]]和[[邁阿密大獎賽|邁阿密大獎賽]]。）<ref>{{Cite web |title=Formula 1: Las Vegas to host grand prix from 2023 - third yearly race in United States |url=https://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/60932994 |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=www.bbc.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220624115733/https://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/60932994 }}</ref> 

==賽道佈局==
賽道是專門為F1大獎賽而設計，已經提出並測試了幾種可能的賽道設計。<ref>{{Cite web |title=F1 ANNOUNCES SATURDAY NIGHT LAS VEGAS GRAND PRIX FOR 2023 |url=https://the-race.com/formula-1/f1-announces-saturday-night-las-vegas-grand-prix-for-2023/ |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=the-race.com |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220605135812/https://the-race.com/formula-1/f1-announces-saturday-night-las-vegas-grand-prix-for-2023/ }}</ref> 最後決定這將是一條6.12公里（3.8英里）的賽道，有14個彎道、3條直道和2個DRS區域。<ref name="circuit">{{Cite web |title=LAS VEGAS GRAND PRIX TRACK LAYOUT: Check out the Las Vegas Grand Prix circuit’s layout |url=https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.revealed-check-out-the-las-vegas-grand-prix-circuits-layout.1xBOUUuDJDtqX4ukNvnHcK.html |access-date=2022-03-31 |website=Formula 1® |language=en |archive-date=2022-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220614005132/https://www.formula1.com/en/latest/article.revealed-check-out-the-las-vegas-grand-prix-circuits-layout.1xBOUUuDJDtqX4ukNvnHcK.html }}</ref>

[[File:Las_Vegas_Street_Circuit_2023.png|thumb]]佈局]]

這個長{{Convert|6.120|km}}的街道賽道有14個彎道和一條長{{Convert|1.920|km}}的大直路。賽道是逆時針行駛，在一個廢棄的停車場做起點（將被重新開發為維修區和圍場區域，並包含永久性賽道）。第一個彎道是一個髮夾彎，之后賽道略微向左彎曲，然後是一個快速向右彎，從永久賽道過渡到城市街道。然後賽車在長{{Convert|800|m|mi}}的Koval Lane行駛，然後進入緩慢的90度右彎，然後進入一個長長的左彎，環繞著新的{{le|MSG球體競技場|MSG Sphere at The Venetian}}並進入金沙大道。然后賽道在金沙大道上經過兩個非常快速的彎道，然後進入緩慢的左彎進入[[拉斯維加斯大道|拉斯維加斯大道]]。這是一個長{{Convert|1.920|km}}的全速路段，有兩條直道和一個輕微的左轉，經過一些拉斯維加斯最著名的酒店和賭場。然后賽道經過一系列緩慢的彎道后進入哈蒙大道，沿著長{{Convert|800|m|mi}}的直道直行，然後通過一個非常快速的左轉完成一圈或回到維修站。<ref name="circuit"/>

